_sText:
Welcome to mg_iolite_multigames! A multigames map made by Lucia and tommy

Featuring 8 fun minigames, a slick minimalist design, soft lighting and 10 music picks.

Featured games are:
  • ScoutzKnivez
  • Soccer
  • Bhop
  • Longjump
  • Deagle (HS)
  • Shotguns
  • Climb
  • Iceskate

Map took a little over a month from start to finish. We hope you enjoy!

Big thanks to: polar., Fudge Packah, Left Twix, pancakes, BOT Nick, Edubb44, maddox, mlpol, Toxic and Ylli for helping out with playtesting!
